                    <p class="flow-text">blargbot is equipped with a system of tags called BBTag,
                        designed to mimic a programming language while still remaining simple.
                        You can use this system as the building-blocks to create your own
                        advanced command system, whether it be through public tags
                        or guild-specific custom commands.</p>
                    <p class="flow-text">Have a suggestion for a tag? I'm all ears! Drop me a
